---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-8 md:px-32 gap-6">
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 justify-between items-center px-8 md:px-32 font-bold mt-6">
        <Card>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">What is a Cold Mix Plant?</h2><br>
            <p class="text-grisP">Cold mix asphalt plants are designed for blending aggregates and asphalt emulsions 
                at ambient temperatures, eliminating the need for heating. Using a pugmill mixer, 
                they ensure a uniform, high-quality mix ideal for a wide range of road maintenance 
                and construction applications.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Precision Dosing for Reliable Results</h2><br>
            <p class="text-grisP">Equipped with material hoppers and adjustable gates, 
                cold mix plants provide precise control over aggregate dosing. This accuracy allows 
                for consistent mix quality and repeatable results, even when using different material 
                types or gradations.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Eco-Friendly Asphalt Solutions</h2><br>
            <p class="text-grisP">Cold mix technology uses lower temperatures and fewer emissions
                 compared to traditional hot mix plants. This makes them a more environmentally 
                 conscious choice, particularly in areas with strict emissions regulations or 
                 urban work zones.</p>
          </Card>
        <Card>
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Built for Mobility and Easy Setup</h2><br>
            <p class="text-grisP">Compact and mobile configurations make cold mix plants easy to 
                transport and set up on any site. With minimal installation requirements, they’re 
                ideal for short-term jobs or shifting from site to site quickly and efficiently.</p>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <GallerySlider slides={binSlides} visibleThumbs={6} client:only />
</div>
